text:
In the file TXFMXPathFilte.hpp (http://santuario.apache.org/c/apiDocs/TXFMXPathFilter_8hpp-source.html) at line 26 and 27 there is an error in the include guard defines. The define in line 27 should have an T as first letter.

#if !defined (TXFMXPATHFILTER_HEADER)
#define XFMXPATHFILTER_HEADER

should be 

#if !defined (TXFMXPATHFILTER_HEADER)
#define TXFMXPATHFILTER_HEADER
